			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "to trigger Greeting -\r\n1. Start the game\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. goto -615 14.169\r\n4. Talk to Kirgrath\r\n\r\nto trigger Mutiny happened - \r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. goto -615 14.169\r\n4. use recon command: SetGlobalOsirisFlag UND_DuergarCamp_State_Mutiny\r\n5. Talk toThudd\r\n\r\nto trigger Nere killed - \r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. goto -615 14.169\r\n4. Destroy the wall (Ctrl-Shift-K)\r\n5. Side with rebels.\r\n6. killcombat.\r\n7. Talk with Thudd\r\n\r\nTo trigger Nere Killed hasmet.\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. goto -615 14.169\r\n4. Talk toThudd\r\n5. Destroy the wall (Ctrl-Shift-K)\r\n6. Side with rebels.\r\n7. killcombat.\r\n8. Talk with Thudd"
				},
