				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Pissed off duergar raider who is standing guard while the gnomes are digging up a collapsed tunnel. He is cursing his superior, saying they should just let him suffocate. The player can make use of this and threathen the duergar, saying they will tell the sergeant unless the duergar gives them money."
				}
